   141Рєњ### Synchronous API (`Result`)
   143Рєњ#### `ok`
   145РєњConstructs an `Ok` variant of `Result`
   146Рєњ
   147Рєњ**Signature:**
   148Рєњ
   149Рєњ```typescript
   150Рєњok<T, E>(value: T): Ok<T, E> { ... }
   151Рєњ```
   152Рєњ
   153Рєњ**Example:**
   154Рєњ
   155Рєњ```typescript
   156Рєњimport { ok } from 'neverthrow'
   157Рєњ
   158Рєњconst myResult = ok({ myData: 'test' }) // instance of `Ok`
   159Рєњ
   160РєњmyResult.isOk() // true
   161РєњmyResult.isErr() // false
   162Рєњ```
   163Рєњ
