   863Рєњ### Asynchronous API (`ResultAsync`) Рђд
   865Рєњ#### `okAsync`
   867РєњConstructs an `Ok` variant of `ResultAsync`
   868Рєњ
   869Рєњ**Signature:**
   870Рєњ
   871Рєњ```typescript
   872РєњokAsync<T, E>(value: T): ResultAsync<T, E>
   873Рєњ```
   874Рєњ
   875Рєњ**Example:**
   876Рєњ
   877Рєњ```typescript
   878Рєњimport { okAsync } from 'neverthrow'
   879Рєњ
   880Рєњconst myResultAsync = okAsync({ myData: 'test' }) // instance of `ResultAsync`
   881Рєњ
   882Рєњconst myResult = await myResultAsync // instance of `Ok`
   883Рєњ
   884РєњmyResult.isOk() // true
   885РєњmyResult.isErr() // false
   886Рєњ```
   887Рєњ
